# Rollback and Ownership (Enterprise AI)

## Ownership
- Product Owner: intent, adoption outcomes, risk acceptance
- Engineering Owner: reliability, deployment, on-call
- Governance/Risk Partner: controls, audit readiness

## Rollback
- Rollback triggers (what conditions force rollback)
- Rollback mechanism (how to disable safely)
- Rollback test cadence (how often you validate it works)
- Communication plan (who is notified and how)
